-- Deutsche Bank Names Alan Ruskin Global Head G-10 Foreign-Exchange Strategy
-- Paul Dobson
-- 2010-07-09T08:47:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-09/deutsche-bank-names-alan-ruskin-global-head-g-10-foreign-exchange-strategy.html

          
          
             Deutsche Bank AG hired  Alan Ruskin 
from Royal Bank of Scotland Group Plc as global head of Group-
of-10 foreign-exchange strategy, it said today in an e-mailed
statement.  
